data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Sierra Foothills! This single story 3760 sq ft beauty boasts 5 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms, with an attached 3-car garage AND Detached 4147 Sq Foot Workshop! Step into luxury with over $280,000 in recent upgrades! The whole house generator ensures peace of mind, while the brand-new roof & owned solar system keep your energy bills low. Imagine summer days by the gorgeous pool, complete with a soothing fountain & Sunset Views- the perfect oasis to relax & unwind. With 4.5 acres of all usable land, there's plenty of room for outdoor activities & exploration on the class 1 Paved El Dorado Walking Trail just outside your fence! Worried about parking? Fear not! There is an abundance of parking for all your family gatherings & events. Inside, discover a beautiful great room leading to spacious covered back deck to drink in the view, huge Center Island in the gourmet kitchen, separate family room & the convenience of a huge indoor laundry room with a dedicated dog washing station for your furry friends! This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss out on the chance to call this slice of paradise yours!
